          </p>
          <p rend="left" id="9c756b1a-c979-4d27-880e-4a906dfec332"><hi style="npnumber">164</hi><pb n="164"/><hi style="npdelimiter"><choice original_editorial_correction="Булг[акову]"><sic>Булг</sic><corr>Булгакову</corr></choice>:</hi><choice original_editorial_correction="Н[а]"><sic>Н</sic><corr>На</corr></choice><choice original_editorial_correction="К[аждый]"><sic>К</sic><corr>Каждый</corr></choice><choice original_editorial_correction="Д[ень]"><sic>Д</sic><corr>День</corr></choice><choice original_editorial_correction="пригото[вить]"><sic>пригото</sic><corr>приготовить</corr></choice>и отправить.</p>
          <p rend="left" id="23fdf27c-945e-4118-b092-d06701bda3b0">Найти длинное<choice original_editorial_correction="пись[мо]"><sic>пись</sic><corr>письмо</corr></choice><choice original_editorial_correction="Ч[ерткова]"><sic>Ч</sic><corr>Черткова</corr></choice>.</p>
